{"tid":687363,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"十大武器之首唔係摺櫈，係....","createTime":"2018-06-02T07:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T09:19:26.000Z","uid":73545,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"80a3a11b51be721c25fa33d44779dda0050dc615","tid":687363,"uid":73545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T07:58:59.000Z","msg":"係呢部呀屌你老母！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/154154_e2e6ad31a1137df329791b159a6b9b8f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F154154_e2e6ad31a1137df329791b159a6b9b8f.png&h=629ebd6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔單只同摺櫈一樣可以坐，<br />\n重可以代步，<br />\n自由穿梭於行人路，<br />\n只要輕輕推個掣就可以撞你老母，<br />\n重危險過女人揸車！<br />\n<br />\n頭先同女朋友自拍，<br />\n條廢老以為我哋影佢，<br />\n佢即刻踩行turbo撞鳩我叫我刪相，<br />\n我：阿婆我冇影你啵！<br />\n婆：你快啲刪！<br />\n我：我真係冇影你啵！<br />\n婆：你唔刪我就報警！<br />\n<br />\n跟住個阿婆企起身去車後面個袋拎電話，<br />\n婆：我報啦！<br />\n我：我屌你你撞鳩我都未計，報啦！睇下邊個啱？<br />\n婆：我報警！我報啦，你再唔刪我報啦！<br />\n我：唔使辛苦你老人家啦，我報。<br />\n<br />\n我一拎起個電話，屌佢直接揸車走咗，<br />\n重快撚過保特，追兩步連車尾燈都見唔到....<br />\n（男人腳圖警告）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/155652_a7feb89d81a5e0fd5f856a5ac3041074.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F155652_a7feb89d81a5e0fd5f856a5ac3041074.png&h=56015d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你依家已經開始瘀瘀黑黑。"},{"pid":"400d07b185d394ca691fd3b5bade858974f7147a","tid":687363,"uid":136763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:00:07.000Z","msg":"太貴 唔普及"},{"pid":"a73da6646a5127272903c3ea2e415f8a263b9c34","tid":687363,"uid":73545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"400d07b185d394ca691fd3b5bade858974f7147a","tid":687363,"uid":136763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018